# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
1. Here we will store the count of every character for this you can use hashmap or frequency array whatever you find easy;
2. Then after this we will find the first character whose frequency is less than k, certainly this characher will not be icluded in the substring 
3. Here we will divide out string int two substring about this character
4. Then we will call the same function on left and right substrings and return the maximum of these two values.

# Approach
